(446, 1, '2017-12-13 11:22:34', '2017-12-13 11:22:34', '<!--themify_builder_static--><h2>Stewart Gooney Online Portfolio</h2>\n \n <a href="http://stewartgooney.info/#about" > Click Here </a> \n <h3><em>&#8220;Be Inspired&#8221;</em></h3>\n \n <img src="http://stewartgooney.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/933956wsm5Fqik.jpg" alt="stewart" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/stewartgooney.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/933956wsm5Fqik.jpg?w=1920 1920w, https://i1.wp.com/stewartgooney.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/933956wsm5Fqik.jpg?resize=300%2C199 300w, https://i1.wp.com/stewartgooney.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/933956wsm5Fqik.jpg?resize=768%2C510 768w, https://i1.wp.com/stewartgooney.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/933956wsm5Fqik.jpg?resize=1024%2C681 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /> \n <h3>About Me</h3> <h6>Hi my name is Stewart and welcome to my Portfolio Website, here you will</h6> <h6>find a collection of my work in both photography and graphic design. I have a</h6> <h6>great passion for photography and graphic design.</h6> <h6>I am a creative individual with good technical knowledge of DSLR camera&#8217;s and the Adobe Creative Suite.</h6> <h6>Im currently studying a BA in Creative Digital Media at the Institute ofTechnology Blanchardstown.Im constantlyworking on design projects plus im working on a drama filmwherei am currently infinal cut editing of a drama called &#8220;Jason&#8221;. The drama is recreatingachapterfromthe book &#8220;The Spinning Heart&#8221;.</h6> <h6>I hope you enjoy looking at my work, if you have any questions feel free to</h6> <h6>contact me. A copy of my CV is available here to <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1EzbfRbaJl2FP_XfNaZyFDke3BBRguDPd/view?usp=sharing">dowload in PDF</a></h6> <p>If you have any queries<a href="http://stewartgooney.info/contact/"> click here</a> I will get back to you a.s.a.p</p>\n \n \n \n \n <h3> Web Design </h3> <p>I have excellent knowledge in website design and development!! Creating wireframes and page layouts on both static and interactive websites.</p> \n \n \n \n \n \n <h3> Photography </h3> <p>Photography is one of my favourite things to do in my free time !! I work with Nikon D3100 and D3200 camera&#8217;s.</p> \n \n \n \n \n \n <h3> Graphic Design </h3> <p>I have excellent knowledge in the Adobe creative Suite, using programs such as Illustrator, InDesign, Photoshop, Dreamweaver, Dimensions, which I use for developing and designing graphical elements !!</p> \n \n <h2>Photography</h2>\n[gallery _orderbyfield="menu_order ID" _orderByField="menu_order ID" ids="36,88,42,43,555,558,559,596,579,599,602,611"]\n \n <iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/247295573" width="640" height="480" title="Game Design" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe> \n \n <h2>Blog</h2>\n <h1>Contact</h1>\n \n Dublin Ireland \n \n Stewartgooney1@gmail.com \n \n 0857609400 \n<h3></h3><iframe frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Dublin+Ireland&amp;t=m&amp;z=7&amp;output=embed&amp;iwloc=near"></iframe><!--/themify_builder_static-->', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2017-12-17 13:55:46', '2017-12-17 13:55:46', '', 0, 'http://stewartgooney.info/?page_id=446', 0, 'page', '', 0),
